casebody.head_matter:
Jacqueline M. KING, Petitioner,
v.
DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA, et al.
No. 19-6629
Supreme Court of the United States.
January 13, 2020
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the District of Columbia Court of Appeals dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
